    - Term: Conversation/0x0100000400000561/Description
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - A striking young woman in a silver body-suit smokes in the hostel hallway. She addresses you as if you were a police officer. You may use your finger pistols for a SUGGESTION red-check. Failure gives you some forewarning about what's going on.
      Flags: 00
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: Conversation/0x0100000400000561/Title
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - WHIRLING F2 / KLAASJE 1
      Flags: 00
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: Conversation/0x010000040000059A/Description
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - 57. Polis Karakolu memuru Teğmen Kim Kitsuragi, seninle bölgeler arası bir çalışma gerçekleştirerek ASILMIŞ ADAMIN gizemini çözmek için aşağıda bekliyor. Anlaşılan 41. Polis Karakolu, "Martinaise"de linç edilen "Whitewater paralı askerinin" soruşturması için seni göndermiş. O zaman sen gerçekten de bir polissin. Kim, sana vakayla ilgili bilgi verdi ve böylece ilişkiniz başladı; hatta muhtemelen biraz kötü başladı ama öyle olmak zorunda değil tabii.
      Flags: 00
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: Conversation/0x010000040000059A/Title
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - WHIRLING / KIM INTRO
      Flags: 00
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: Conversation/0x01000004000005AF/Description
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - Teğmen Kitsuragi önce Whirling‑in‑Rags'in müdürüyle konuşmanı önerdi. Garte, bu bölgeye ve yaşanan olaya dair çok geniş bilgilere sahip. Onun yanına daha sonra geri döneceksin. Ancak kendisi aynı zamanda oda ücretini ödemeni ve "hasarı karşılamanı" isteyerek sana sorun da çıkarıyor. Bu durum seni iyi göstermiyor.
      Flags: 00
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: Conversation/0x01000004000005AF/Title
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - WHIRLING F1 / GARTE
      Flags: 00
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: Conversation/0x0100000400000618/Description
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - 'A corpse hangs from the pine-tree: a middle aged man in white armour boots and tighty whities. A medium PERCEPTION white-check lets you find a bullet hole in the back of his mouth, a low LOGIC white check that he was killed before hanging. A low THOUGHT CABINET w-c sees that the bullet is antique.'
      Flags: 00
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: Conversation/0x0100000400000618/Title
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - YARD / HANGED MAN
      Flags: 00
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: Conversation/0x0100000400000653/Description
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - An easy PERCEPTION check highlights a scattering of bullet holes in the wall. Pass a medium VISUAL CALCULUS and the interact appears as a ghostly mass execution perpetrated by dotted lines against a row of figures facing the wall. Either way, dialogue with the object has you and Lt Kitsuragi figure out it was an execution after the amphibious assault. You may relive it as an INLAND EMPIRE dream sequence later.
      Flags: 00
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: Conversation/0x0100000400000653/Title
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - WESTCOAST / EXECUTIONS VISCAL
      Flags: 00
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: Conversation/0x01000004000006C5/Description
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - "Meeting Klaasje again, on the roof\n 0) Intro\n 1) Your name and \n 2) why u here? (orbs and drugs from room) \n 3) Wildflower\n 5) did you hear me night before / last time we saw\n 6) Looking for Ruby"
      Flags: 00
      Languages_Touch: []
