    - Term: Conversation/0x0100005800002570/Description
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - "By inspecting the bullet, you can find out that:\n1. The bullet came from a breech-loaded rifle.\n2. The bullet was shot from some distance, so this was probably not a mercy kill (white check.)\n3. The rifle used was a model mass-produced during the revolutionary war, and the surplus rifles/ammo are still a favourite with third-world guerrillas and Jamrock bangers."
      Flags: 00
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: Conversation/0x0100005800002570/Title
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
